            <div class="article">
                Cyberpunk: Edgerunners tells a standalone, 10-episode story about a street kid trying to survive
                in a technology and body modification-obsessed city of the future. Having everything to lose,
                he chooses to stay alive by becoming an edgerunner — a mercenary outlaw also known as a cyberpunk.
            </div>

