        <h2>Story</h2>
        <p>
            In the aftermath of a personal tragedy, David Martinez chooses to take control of his own life by
            becoming an edgerunner and entering the criminal underworld of Night City. Cyberpunk: Edgerunners
            asks just how far you can go to overcome your physical and emotional limits.
        </p>

        <h3>Creators</h3>
        <p>
            Cyberpunk: Edgerunners is an award-winning Netflix anime created in collaboration between CD PROJEKT RED
            and Studio TRIGGER. Known for works including Little Witch Academia and Promare, they brought Night City
            to life with style and fire.
        </p>

